The work ethic and drive is undeniable. We’ve distributed $552,000 worth of free essential resources to 43,000 people. 😳

@collectivefocushub is an all-volunteer organization working month-to-month to pay the bills. This work is not easy, it’s not cheap and it’s not for the faint of heart. 😮‍💨

If you have anything extra this holiday season or you’re just looking to give back please visit the first link on my page. 👀

Our goal this week is to raise $5,000 through $5-$25 donations. Pour out what you can and be open to receiving love right back!🤞🏾❤️

lil bro! you were already the person you wanted to be. we laughed yelled and cried. honestly I had some deep cries over this and will definitely cry plenty more. I’m happy to have taken you on an experience that reaffirmed your commitment and dedication to this life of music. You’ve impacted many lives, including mine and inevitably you will impact so many more. I need you to know that I know you’re helping guide us. Say hi to your auntie and the rest of your family up there, they needed to reconnect! & YOU BETTER SAVE ME SOME PANCAKES IN HEAVEN. 
You forever in my spirit twin, fly high and be free. 
Rest in Love❤️‍🩹
